Bug Fix & Feature Update Plan
Issue 1: Emails not sending on Vercel
Root Cause: The Next.js API route was attempting to send the email "asynchronously" without waiting for the promise to resolve (sendTicketEmail(ticket).catch(...)). Serverless functions on Vercel immediately terminate execution once a response is returned. The email sending process was likely being killed before it could finish connecting to the SMTP server. Fix: I will update the code to await the sendTicketEmail function, ensuring the email is sent before the serverless function returns the response.

Issue 2: Deleting Incomplete Transactions
Request: Add the ability to delete transactions that weren't completed. Plan: I will add a new secure DELETE API endpoint and update the Admin UI to include a delete button for pending or rejected tickets.

